com.google.gwt.core.ext.linker.impl
Class PermutationsUtil

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gwt.core.ext.linker.impl.PermutationsUtil

public class PermutationsUtil
extends java.lang.Object

A utility class to help linkers generate a list of permutation mappings and and then either output them to javascript code which selects the correct permutation, or to a file which can be parsed by server side code.

propMapsByPermutation

protected java.util.SortedMap<PermutationsUtil.PermutationId,java.util.List<java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String>>> propMapsByPermutation
This maps each unique permutation to the property settings for that compilation. A single compilation can have multiple property settings if the compiles for those settings yielded the exact same compiled output.
